## Category Analysis Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define category boundaries: What products/services are in and out
- [ ] 2. Map market structure: Fragmented, consolidated, monopolistic
- [ ] 3. Identify key players: Market leaders, challengers, niche players
- [ ] 4. Analyze trends: What's changing in how the category is defined or delivered?
- [ ] 5. Assess growth: Category growth rate, margin structure, seasonality
- [ ] 6. Consumer behavior: How do buyers choose within this category?
- [ ] 7. Identify opportunities: White space, underserved needs, emerging segments

## Key Inputs
- Category: {{category_name}}
- Geographic scope: {{geography}}
- Client/brand: {{brand_name}}
- Competitors: {{competitors}}
